        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "THE DISNEY FROZEN DIARY WITH LOCK COMES WITH UNIQUE DESIGN YOU WILL LOVE – Little girls would love this frozen-themed personal diary with padlock & key. The blue journal has the Frozen characters splashed on the cover reminding your little Frozen fan of Queen Elsa, Princess Anna & Olaf. Let your kid freely express their innermost thoughts & feelings through 60 blank pages of this lockable cute diary.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "THE FROZEN JOURNAL IS PERFECT FOR FROZEN & DISNEY FANS – Every personal thought is kept safe with this secret journal for girls & encourage kids to organize their emotions & thoughts through creative writing. A safe space for kids to dream, to explore their creativity, to strengthen themselves after bad days, and remind them of the good ones. This locking diary would make a great first diary to start collecting personal journals.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "INCLUDED WITH THE PURCHASE OF THE LOCKABLE FROZEN NOTEBOOK DIARY - Includes 1 Frozen Diary with 1 Padlock, 2 Keys, & 1 fluffy Pom Pen that comes in a card packaging. A cute hardcover Disney journal that's travel-sized & can fit in any of your kid's bags making it accessible for scribbling & doodling. Journal keeping is great to boost writing skills & creativity. Disney's Frozen diary has 60 sheets of blank pages and measures 5x7 inches.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "HIGH-QUALITY FROZEN SECRET DIARY WITH LOCK FOR GIRLS – Frozen's secret safe diary is made of premium quality of paper so you can write and doodle neatly without hesitations. Meanwhile, the fluffy pen that comes with the secret journal features a light blue pom at the top making it super fun to pen down creative ideas. Your little one would love to fill this 60 page kids diary with their random scribbles, sketches, pictures & good memories!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "IDEAL USE FOR THE FROZEN LOCKING JOURNAL FOR GIRLS – Unlock their creativity, build up their writing skills & emotional awareness as they record their day, doodle, write letters, sketch, make a list of goals & plans, or even make a scrapbook out of this Frozen locking diary for girls! Best part about the locked diary is that they can immediately write down all their spontaneous ideas that they would always keep this at hand.",
